    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I heard Dr. #p308# has finished her fossil research. Maybe I should go and see the results."
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I met Dr. #p308# again. She told me the research was finished and explained it to me, then asked me to take the research report and deliver it to Dr. #p512# in #m10004000#. Dr. Betty also informed me that if I take #b20 #t4000011#s, 15 #t4000015#s, 1 #t4031075#, and 1 pair of #t1032002##k, Dr. #p512# would be really happy. "
    },
    "2": {
      "_dirName": "2",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I delivered Dr. #p308#'s #t4031074# to Dr. #p512# in #m10004000#. Along with the report, I also gave him the #t4000011#s, #t4000015#s, #t4031075#, and #t1032002#. In return, Dr. Winston gave me the #t1032015#."
    },
